    author = "Uddin, Lucina Q and Mooshagian, Eric and Zaidel, Eran and Scheres, Anouk and Margulies, Daniel S and Kelly, A M Clare and Shehzad, Zarrar and Adelstein, Jonathan S and Castellanos, F Xavier and Biswal, Bharat B and Milham, Michael P",
