    author = "Filippi, Massimo and Agosta, Federica and Scola, Elisa and Canu, Elisa and Magnani, Giuseppe and Marcone, Alessandra and Valsasina, Paola and Caso, Francesca and Copetti, Massimiliano and Comi, Giancarlo and Cappa, Stefano F and Falini, Andrea",
