    author = "Paakki, Jyri-Johan and Rahko, Jukka and Long, Xiangyu and Moilanen, Irma and Tervonen, Osmo and Nikkinen, Juha and Starck, Tuomo and Remes, Jukka and Hurtig, Tuula and Haapsamo, Helena and Jussila, Katja and Kuusikko-Gauffin, Sanna and Mattila, Marja-Leena and Zang, Yufeng and Kiviniemi, Vesa",
